{"tid":758711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 意想不到!  震驚700 萬人的CCtvb 訃聞部的報導範文竟然係 ...?","createTime":"2018-07-28T03:38:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T13:09:35.000Z","uid":51701,"like":558,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"3b44ebc3a004c4da0898c9da7976d33892ebcad8","tid":758711,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T03:38:11.000Z","msg":"政府努力壓抑樓價 (事實: 政府有份推高)<br />\n<br />\n侵侵內憂外患 (習種先係)<br />\n<br />\n歐洲有意乞求中國圍攻美國(<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n美國交通意外二十人受傷 (支那13 億人口0 意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n危地馬拉6 級地震, 幾百人死 (支那一個風已經成個市滅左)<br />\n<br />\n建制派要求加人工減工時增福利(讚成, 但否決)<br />\n<br />\n10 分鐘轉播口交部 (強烈 ...)<br />\n<br />\n分析指 消息人士透露 有評論認為 日本媒體引述<br />\n<br />\n支那掠影 山西農民自製火箭 上海學生補習費超越香港 河南農民拾百圓不昧 廣西老人慶祝過百歲<br />\n<br />\n環乳掠影 哈薩克民眾喜迎西氣東輸 阿富漢難民受中國救援 剛果基建由支那幫手<br />\n<br />\n最後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中國或成最大贏家</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/113451_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F113451_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=80fc3960&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/113452_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F113452_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=63b58ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/28/113454_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F28%2F113454_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=7e57e7c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a080c237b581174a4882b3ea7654bb